Here's the optimized version of the `AclAuthorizer.scala` file addressing the performance issue mentioned regarding the filtering of ACLs. The changes focus on ensuring that we only iterate over the relevant collections for filtering rather than processing all of them, which should provide significant performance improvements in scenarios with a large number of topics and ACLs. 

